body:
This release includes an important fix for Windows version and enhancement for SMTP authentication.

## What's Changed
* fix(windows): bug in command construction with powershell/cmd.exe by @yottahmd in https://github.com/dagu-org/dagu/pull/1445
* fix(mail): add STARTTLS and LOGIN auth support for SMTP by @yottahmd in https://github.com/dagu-org/dagu/pull/1446


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/dagu-org/dagu/compare/v1.25.0...v1.25.1
name: v1.25.1
